OL,3,CCouncil tax rise agreed in
OL,4,CPembrokeshire after last-minute change
OL,5,Cto plans
OL,7,FPembrokeshire County Council have
OL,8,Fvoted to increase council tax by 12.5%
OL,9,Ffor the forthcoming financial year,
OL,10,Fadding #167.44 on to the average
OL,11,Fannual household bill.
OL,13,FIt comes after a last-minute change to
OL,14,Fplans as the rate was set to rise even
OL,15,Fmore, with three options on the table
OL,16,Fprior to March 7 being an increase of
OL,17,F16.31%, 18.94% or even 20.98%.
