OL,7,FHe said that would see a weekly
OL,8,Fcouncil tax increase for the average
OL,9,Fproperty of #3.22, or #167.86 a year.
OL,10,FThe amendment was backed by 30 votes
OL,11,Fto 26, with one abstention.
OL,13,FThe final council tax bill for
OL,14,Fresidents would be higher than this as
OL,15,Ftown and community council precepts
OL,16,Fand the police precept would be added;
OL,17,Fwith second home-owners and empty
OL,18,Fproperty owners facing even higher
OL,19,Fbills as both have a premium rate.
