OL,4,CPembrokeshire after last-minute change
OL,5,Cto plans
OL,7,FThe premium rate on second homes for
OL,8,Fthe next financial year is 200%,
OL,9,Feffectively a treble rate, with a more
OL,10,Fcomplicated approach on empty
OL,11,Fproperties that increases the longer
OL,12,Fthey remain empty.
OL,14,FThe 12.5% rise comes on top of
OL,15,Fprevious increases of 12.5%, 9.92%,
OL,16,F5%, 3.75%, 5% and 7.5%.
